2. Strategy — Validation & Encryption

Where it applies:
Validation stages across pipeline (pre-store, post-store, handshake validation)

Purpose:
Swap validation/encryption logic without conditionals.

Template:

from abc import ABC, abstractmethod
class ValidationStrategy(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def validate(self, data):
        pass
class PasswordValidation(ValidationStrategy):
    def validate(self, password):
        return len(password) >= 8
class SSHKeyValidation(ValidationStrategy):
    def validate(self, keypair):
        return "public" in keypair and "private" in keypair
class Validator:
    def __init__(self, strategy: ValidationStrategy):
        self.strategy = strategy
    def validate(self, data):
        return self.strategy.validate(data)

