5. Repository — Credential Storage

Where it applies:
Storage layer (file system, DB, vault, etc.)

Purpose:
Abstract persistence and enforce secure handling.

Template:

from abc import ABC, abstractmethod
class CredentialRepository(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def save(self, credential):
        pass
    @abstractmethod
    def load(self, credential_id):
        pass
class InMemoryCredentialRepository(CredentialRepository):
    def __init__(self):
        self.store = {}
    def save(self, credential):
        cid = len(self.store) + 1
        self.store[cid] = credential
        return cid
    def load(self, credential_id):
        return self.store.get(credential_id)

