6. Facade — Client Interface

Where it applies:
Entry point for Client A

Purpose:
Hide orchestration complexity behind a simple API.

Template:

class CredentialService:
    def __init__(self, factory, validator, repository):
        self.factory = factory
        self.validator = validator
        self.repository = repository
    def onboard_password(self, raw_password):
        credential = self.factory.create(raw_password)
        if not self.validator.validate(raw_password):
            raise ValueError("Validation failed")
        return self.repository.save(credential)

