8. Command — Pipeline Operations

Where it applies:
Each pipeline step (generate → validate → encrypt → store)

Purpose:
Encapsulate actions for queuing, logging, retrying.

Template:

from abc import ABC, abstractmethod
class Command(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def execute(self):
        pass
class GenerateCredentialCommand(Command):
    def __init__(self, factory, data):
        self.factory = factory
        self.data = data
    def execute(self):
        return self.factory.create(self.data)
class ValidateCommand(Command):
    def __init__(self, validator, data):
        self.validator = validator
        self.data = data
    def execute(self):
        return self.validator.validate(self.data)

